stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Submit
    Submit: OffloadEngine.submit(job, backend="gpu-opencl")
    Submit --> KernelBuild
    KernelBuild: compile OpenCL / CUDA kernel

    state KernelBuild <<choice>>
    KernelBuild --> DeviceRun: build succeeded
    KernelBuild --> CPUFallback: build failed / device missing

    DeviceRun: enqueue + dispatch on GPU
    DeviceRun --> DeviceResult
    DeviceResult: OffloadResult(ok=True, backend="gpu-opencl")
    DeviceResult --> [*]

    CPUFallback: invoke deepview.offload.kdf:pbkdf2_sha256\non host (process pool)
    CPUFallback --> CPUResult
    CPUResult: OffloadResult(ok=True,\nbackend="process",\noutput includes fallback=True tag)
    CPUResult --> [*]

    note right of CPUFallback
        Guarantees forward progress:
        GPU backends never hard-fail.
        Callers see OffloadJobCompletedEvent
        with backend field reflecting
        the actual executor.
    end note
